<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f7; color: #51545E; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    h1 { color: #333333; }
    .code { display: block; background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #333; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 20px; }
    p { line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome, {{firstName}}!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for registering. To complete your registration, use the verification code below:</p>
    <span class="code">{{code}}</span>
    <p>If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" class="btn">Go to Main Page</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
